node.text: We’re a bunch of nerds and we like nerd stuff. That includes collecting stuff that represents stuff we like. Introducing Stocky! The new collectible from Donut. We’ve been working on this for over two years and are so stoked to finally share it with you guys. We’re live on kickstarter right now and super close to our goal. If you like nerd stuff too go check it out!

node.text: Gus Johnson came by and helped me test weird Amazon products on this jetta. Jokes were made. Laughs were had. @tendergreens was consumed. New D List is on the tube. Please watch it. This is my job. If I don’t get enough views I don’t get to have Christmas. 📷 @cleveralias

node.text: This killer-chiller and I just got the keys to our own plot of dirt. As land owners, we’re both looking forward to being allowed to vote for the first time.
